A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of a sleek web server tower in a dark neon-lit environment, with glowing parasitic organisms crawling across its surface like bioluminescent creatures. The parasites appear as small, translucent worm-like beings with circuit patterns inside them, leaving trails of corrupted data visualized as dripping neon pink and toxic green liquid. The server has exposed panels revealing clean blue circuitry being overtaken by these invaders. In the background, holographic warning indicators pulse red through the hazy atmosphere. The scene is bathed in contrasting cool blues and threatening magentas, creating an ominous technological atmosphere that suggests digital infection and hidden threats lurking within seemingly normal systems.
